data.description: Stunning and Spacious 3-Bedroom Single Family Home in Clinton Neighborhood  Welcome to 6304 Florenc Ct, a sensational property that perfectly combines style, comfort, and an exceptional location in the desirable Clinton neighborhood. This remarkable home boasts an impressive array of features, including an open, modern, and white kitchen, and a spacious backyard with a brand-new fence.  As you step inside this charming abode, you will be greeted by a beautifully designed layout that maximizes both function and coziness. The open-concept kitchen, with its sleek and modern finishes, is a culinary enthusiast's dream come true. Cook up gourmet meals effortlessly while enjoying the abundance of natural light that floods the space.  One of the standout features of this property is the spacious back yard, offering an ideal oasis for relaxation, entertainment, and play. The newly installed fence ensures privacy and adds a touch of elegance to the outdoor space, creating the perfect setting for hosting memorable gatherings or simply unwinding in your own retreat.  In addition to its remarkable interior and outdoor spaces, this fantastic home offers several exceptional amenities that are sure to enhance your living experience. Imagine taking a refreshing dip in the inviting pool during summer days or cozying up by the fireplace during chilly winter evenings. With a garage providing convenience and security for your vehicles, this residence truly caters to your every need.
